---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Map from '../components/Map.astro';
import ImageGallery from '../components/ImageGallery.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Amenities | Palma Miami Beach | Luxury Condos in Miami Beach"
  description="At Palma, quality reigns supreme, with every amenity thoughtfully curated for your lifestyle. View our services and amenities, including the Palma Beach Club."
>
  <PageHero videoSrc="/videos/neighborhood-video.mp4" title="Neighborhood" />
  <section class="text-box no-bg">
    <p>
      In the heart of Miami Beach lies a neighborhood where life unfolds with
      elegance and excitement. Fine dining and vibrant entertainment fill the
      streets, while the Aquatic Center and Miami Beach Tennis Center cater to
      your active side. The nearby Normandy Shores Golf Club offers lush greens
      for a serene escape, and beach volleyball courts provide a sandy
      playground for spirited matches.
    </p>
    <p>
      As twilight falls, jazz concerts fill the air, creating moments of pure
      magic. For adventure seekers, jet ski and kayak rentals promise thrilling
      water escapades. The famed Miami Beach Boardwalk invites you on a scenic
      journey from your doorstep to the lively South Pointe Park.
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="full-width-img">
    <img src="/images/neighborhood/palma-view.webp" />
  </section>
  <Map />
  <ImageGallery />
</Layout>
